{"article_id":"zvDwHKc6sE0smS1k","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hurricane Irma set records","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"before downgrading to a Category 2","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"with winds weakening to 100 mph","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"when it crossed over the Tampa-St.Petersburg region .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Before hitting Florida ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"it brutalized the Caribbean as a Category 5","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and washed over the Florida Keys as a Category 4 hurricane .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"As it moved north ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Irma 's enormous size lashed Florida from coast to coast ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"stretching out an amazing 415 miles across ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"but it weakened Monday to a tropical storm with life-threatening storm surges , dangerous wind and heavy rains .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The once-Category 5 storm had lost some of its oomph","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"approaching the U.S. mainland","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"after running into the northern Cuba coast .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Its winds dropped to a potent 115 mph","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"when it made its second landfall on Marco Island , down from its 185 mph peak .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Overall , the storm submerged streets in Florida ,","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"caused power outages for millions","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"and snapped huge construction cranes in Miami .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"But faith was on display","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"as the storm was threatening into Florida .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"President Donald Trump bowed in prayer with his Cabinet","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"as Vice President Mike Pence opened an emergency planning meeting with prayer at Camp David on Saturday .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"RELATED :","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Bible Studies at the White House :","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Who 's Inside This Spiritual Awakening ?","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"RELATED :","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Faith Leaders Pray for Trump in Oval Office ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Enjoy 'Open Door ' at White House","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Earlier , the White House had released this statement from President Trump :","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"`` The President and his Cabinet ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"meeting at Camp David ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"continue to receive regular updates on Hurricanes Irma and Jose .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"FEMA is leading the Federal effort","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to coordinate support to the impacted States and U.S . Territories .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"The President and First Lady are keeping all the people","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"impacted by Hurricanes Harvey and Irma in their thoughts and prayers","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and urge everyone to listen to and follow the safety instructions of local authorities . ''","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Trump also called on everyone in the storm 's path to count their lives greater than their possessions","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and `` get out of its way . ''","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"property can be replaced ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"but people ca n't ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"all of America grieves for those","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"who have died .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Meanwhile , some Florida residents prayed","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and sang `` The Great I Am '' on the beaches","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"as Irma approached .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"This is incredible ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"some residents","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"singing `` The Great I Am '' on a Miami Beach","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"before # irma comes through","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"pic.twitter.com/nUNXlhr0D","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"7 - Adam ن","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"( @ adambeamer )","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"September 10 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"as the threat of storm surge threatened the state , for the Keys all the way up through Tampa ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Florida 's Governor Rick Scott called for prayer .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" I don ' t see prayer as a last resort ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"it should always be a first resort , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"said Florida Governor Rick Scott .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"`` Pray , pray for everybody in Florida , ''","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"he said on Fox News Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Weekend Coverage Below :","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"Florida Power & Light says","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"it will be weeks , not days ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"before electricity is fully restored","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"because of the damage","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"being done by Irma .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Nearly 7 million homes and businesses lost power","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"as Irma climbed the Florida mainland .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"As Irma made its way through the Florida region","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"storm surge was a big concern .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"A storm surge is when waters from the ocean and nearby bodies of water are pushed onto dry land .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"In Miami , there were reports of waist-deep water .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Nearly two feet of water have flooded the streets in the Brickell area .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"The Weather Channel ' s Mike Seidel tweeted this video of a storm surge there .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Brickell area in # Miami","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"taking the surge from # Irma .","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"It 's as deep as 2 ' at SE 12th St. & Brickell Ave.","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"pic.twitter.com/UAhcDLij6N","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"- Mike Seidel","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"( @ mikeseidel )","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"September 10 , 2017","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"\" It ' s bad","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"it ' s nasty here .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"We ' re not even getting the direct hit , \"","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Senator Marco Rubio , R-FL , told Fox News .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"The storm officially made landfall in the Florida Keys a little after 9 am .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"In addition to the storm surge of more than 10 feet there , the chain of islands is still being hit by extremely strong winds .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Meanwhile , President Trump approved Disaster Declaration for Florida and Puerto Rico","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and made additional assistance available for the U.S. Virgin Islands .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"A last minute shift west sent Hurricane Irma heading towards the Tampa Bay and St. Pete area .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Authorities warned nearly seven million people in the Southeast to evacuate .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"That number included 6.4 million in Florida alone .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Irma ran along the northern coast of Cuba Saturday ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"downing power lines and trees","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"and blocking roads .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Thousands of people in the Caribbean raced to find shelter .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Twenty-four people lost their lives in the storm","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"as it barrelled through that region .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"As Irma neared south Florida ,","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Gov . Rick Scott was warning people to follow evacuation orders .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"More than 6 million people were warned to leave their homes ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"and more than 160,000 people took refuge in emergency shelters .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Reporter Gary Lane talks with contributor Chuck Holton about the situation in the shelters .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Gov . Scott added","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"that those","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"who failed to leave the state Friday night","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"would have to ride out the storm at their own risk .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"`` It 's going to be very difficult to survive this","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"if you 're in the Keys , ''","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"he warned during a Saturday morning interview with The Weather Channel .","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"`` I 'm begging you to get out . ''","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Taking his own advice ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Scott and his family evacuated their beachside mansion along the Gulf Coast .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"Hundreds of thousands of Floridians have fled the state ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"clogging its major highways ,","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"but the governor says","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"traffic officials decided not to reverse the direction of southbound lanes","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"because gas and supplies must still move south .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Saturday afternoon , officials allowed motorists to use emergency lanes","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"to speed up the pace .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"Scott is stressing","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"the powerful storm could be a historic disaster .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"`` Remember","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Hurricane Andrew is one of the worst storms in the history of Florida .","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"This storm is much worse , ''","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"Scott said .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Federal Emergency Management Agency chief Brock Long has this advice for people in Irma 's path :","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"`` Get out '' now !","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"Georgia 's Gov . Nathan Deal is urging more than half a million state coastal residents to evacuate","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"before Irma hits .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Irma is the strongest hurricane","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"ever recorded in the Atlantic Ocean .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"When it was still packing 185-175 mile per hour winds ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"it devastated small northern Caribbean islands like Saint Martin and Barbuda .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Here 's what Irma did to St. Martin .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"This amazing footage from the storm shows residents","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"trying to rescue people","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"trapped in a flipped-over bus .","depth":16},{"id":143,"text":"It comes about halfway through :","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"Gaston Brown , prime minister of Antigua and Barbuda , said","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"the country has been decimated .","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"`` It was the worst time in all my life .","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"I would not like to see a hurricane like this again , ''","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"one island resident said .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"`` We were praying the whole time , ''","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"one island visitor said ,","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"standing next to her injured friend in the hospital .","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"In Puerto Rico , Irma left nearly a million people without power","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"and it could be four to six months in some areas","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"before its restored .","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"And here in the U.S. , the National Weather Service warns","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"that some `` locations","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"hit by Irma","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"could be uninhabitable for weeks or months '' due to powerful winds ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"and that `` structural damage to buildings ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"with many washing away ''","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"is possible in some coastal areas .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"Florida is the main state in Irma 's path","depth":3},{"id":163,"text":"where huge numbers of people are evacuating","depth":4},{"id":164,"text":"and getting ready for the monster storm .","depth":4},{"id":165,"text":"And 's Operation Blessing has been stocking up for its relief and humanitarian aid as well .","depth":4},{"id":166,"text":"OB already has dozens of tractor trailer loads of water and food at its warehouse in Ocala , Florida ,","depth":5},{"id":167,"text":"and has been in contact with Florida pastors","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"they 've worked with over the years","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"as it prepares to help those","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"who will need it in Irma 's aftermath .","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"Meanwhile , Operation Blessing continues to aid the flooded residents in Harvey 's aftermath in Texas .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":343,"left":333,"right":342,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":333,"left":200,"right":332,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":200,"left":190,"right":199,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":187,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":178,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":175,"right":177,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":0,"right":174,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":1,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":4,"right":176,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":181,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":180,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":7,"right":179,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":179,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"ela